PEI Kenya: Expected project outputs include:
•	Strengthened Understanding of Poverty and Environmental Linkages Within Government Ministries, Institutions, and other Stakeholders;  
•	Strengthened national Capacity in Economic Valuation of Environment and Natural Resources and integrated (economic, social, and environment) Assessment Methods; 
•	Capacity of Key Stakeholders Strengthened to Integrate Poverty Environment Linkages in Sector and District Development Plans and Budgets and Monitoring Systems;  
•	Strengthened Community Capacity for Sustainable Utilization of Environment and Natural Resources; and 
•	Support Provided for Coordination and Tracking of Environment Components of the District Development Plans and MDGs
